<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (ạ̉mr ạ̹lhy .. bʿzy wjạhy .. wqlby mʿạh mtsẖjʿ
 ạ̉nạ mạsk .. fy wʿwd ạlbrkẗ .. ạlly btrfʿ wtsẖbʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- (rạḥ ạ̉qwl lạ̉ .. wạ̉qf btẖbạt .. qdạm ạlmgẖryạt
 whạqạwm ạ̹blys .. whạqwl lh .. zmnk wlãy̱ wfạt
 2- (ạ̹lhy mlạny .. brwḥ ạlqwẗ .. msẖ rwḥ ạlʿbwdyẗ
 ạ̉slwb ḥyạty .. ạ̉ʿysẖ ywmạty .. fy qdạsẗ ḥqyqyẗ)2
 3- (bạlslṭạn ạlrwḥy .. hạkml .. nạẓr lly fdạny
 kl jswr .. ạlsẖr ạlʿạtyẗ .. hạksrhạ bạ̹ymạny)2
 4- (ḥty̱ ạ̹n kẖwrt .. fy lḥẓẗ ḍʿf .. ymyn ạ̹lhy btrfʿ
 ạsm yswʿ .. brj ḥṣyn .. ạ̉jry ʿlyh wạ̉tmnʿ)2</lyrics>
